org.jasig.cas.adaptors.trusted.authentication.principal

Class PrincipalBearingPrincipalResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jasig.cas.authentication.principal.PersonDirectoryPrincipalResolver
      • org.jasig.cas.adaptors.trusted.authentication.principal.PrincipalBearingPrincipalResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PrincipalResolver

    @Component(value="trustedPrincipalResolver")
public final class PrincipalBearingPrincipalResolver
extends PersonDirectoryPrincipalResolver
    Extracts the Principal out of PrincipalBearingCredential. It is very simple to resolve PrincipalBearingCredential to a Principal since the credentials already bear the ready-to-go Principal.
    Since:
    3.0.0
